Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  莉莉考上大学的话  想去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美聪你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.79,0:00:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西藏吧  还有印度尼西亚  泰国  越南  土耳其
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃及  突尼斯  西班牙  葡萄牙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那个…摩洛哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有钱就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:35.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背包笨蛋—美聪  大学可别中途退学哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉要去欧洲吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.54,0:00:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去佛罗伦萨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.30,0:00:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去美术馆感受一下义大利文艺复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.11,0:00:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看教会建筑  听听歌剧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.71,0:00:47.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有钱就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.01,0:00:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闲人贵妇—莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是贵妇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份平静感就已经很贵妇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.79,0:00:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一男一女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.90,0:00:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.82,0:00:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说过不要吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.97,0:01:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  英语复习还要继续吗？或者算了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:07.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要继续
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业了去冲绳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是先毕业了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过没有钱就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:50.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.98,0:02:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得起来…给沙英做点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.46,0:04:10.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美聪还真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝麻？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.42,0:04:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芝麻…芝麻…芝麻…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安  沙英
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.29,0:04:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  是不是有什么黑色的东西掉在走廊上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:32.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.81,0:04:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙英  小寻  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.03,0:04:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉学姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美聪学姐  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美聪  你又在做什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的题目是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊  时间的视觉化  或者说是行为的意识化之类的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在探究艺术的可能性啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.03,0:05:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为是在弄巫术呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美聪  浪费食物是不对的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后要好好清理干净
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是素描
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（素描）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.77,0:05:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可选主题也是重点之一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然选我也是没问题的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,题目是…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“冬日的窗边少女”怎么样？
